    <p>DASH & LILY (M18) Net­flix</p>
    <p>Dash (Austin Abrams) is al­ways cyn­i­cal, while Lily (Mi­dori Fran­cis) is per­ma­nently op­ti­mistic.</p>
    <p>The pair (both above) dis­cover that they may have a lot more in com­mon than they think when they bond over a shared diary in New York’s Strand Book Store.</p>
    <p>The ro­man­tic com­edy se­ries, redo­lent with mistle­toe and win­try scenes, is based on young-adult novel se­ries Dash & Lily’s Book Of Dares.</p>

